pen_source\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_open_source\">Clustering/Distributed mode</h2>\r\nWith Gatling FrontLine’s clustering (or distributed) mode, you can run tests with a large and worldwide audience.\r\n\r\nGatling FrontLine will deploy your load injectors, close the instances after the test and aggregate your results live.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/5\" el_class=\"column_image_open_source no_radius\"][vc_single_image image=\"464\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"image_open_source\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"section_table_get_started\"][vc_row el_class=\"row_table_get_started\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_table_get_started\" style=\"text-align: center;\">What are the differences</h2>\r\n<p class=\"sub_title_table_get_started\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Between Gatling Open Source and Gatling Frontline?</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html el_class=\"row_inner_table_differences\"]JTVCdGFibGUlMjBpZCUzRDElMjAlMkYlNUQ=[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Are you convinced ?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Go ahead and try Gatling Frontline for free!</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"column_button_convinced\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_btn title=\"Start your evaluation\" align=\"right\" el_class=\"violet_button\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"column_button_convinced\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_btn title=\"Watch demo\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"far fa-play-circle\" add_icon=\"true\" el_class=\"white_button_with_border\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"section_newsletter\"][vc_row el_class=\"row_newsletter\"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_newsletter_top\"]\r\n<p class=\"title_newsletter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Stay in the know!</p>\r\n<p class=\"join_newsletter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Join 10K+ subscribers