st of the cloud providers of the market: Amazon Web Services, Google Cloud Platform, Microsoft Azure, Digital Ocean and the cloud providers based on OpenStack (Rackspace, OVH…).</p>\r\n<p class=\"desc_enterprise\">We also support OpenShift and Kubernetes deployments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"desc_enterprise\">Gatling FrontLine will do everything: open the instance, close the instance after the test and aggregate the results. You configure everything through Gatling FrontLine’s interface.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"row_top_solutions\"][vc_column width=\"2/5\" el_class=\"column_text_open_source\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_open_source\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_open_source\">Clustering/Distributed mode</h2>\r\nWith Gatling FrontLine’s clustering (or distributed) mode, you can run tests with a large and worldwide audience.\r\n\r\nGatling FrontLine will deploy your load injectors, close the instances after the test and aggregate your results live.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/5\" el_class=\"column_image_open_source no_radius\"][vc_single_image image=\"458\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"image_open_source\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"row_bottom_solutions\"][vc_column width=\"3/5\" el_class=\"column_image_enterprise\"][vc_single_image image=\"461\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" el_class=\"image_enterprise\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/5\" el_class=\"column_text_enterprise\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_enterprise\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_enterprise\">Continuous integration</h2>\r\n<p class=\"desc_enterprise\">You can integrate Gatling FrontLine with your Continuous Integration solution. We have official plugins for Jenkins, Bamboo (Atlassian) and TeamCity (Jetbrains). You can trigger your tests, schedule them and get notified of any performance regressions.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"Start for free\" el_class=\"violet_button\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"row_top_solutions\"][vc_column width=\"2/5\" el_class=\"column_text_open_source\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_open_source\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_open_source\">Clustering/Distributed mode</h2>\r\nWith Gatling FrontLine’s clustering (or distributed) mode, you can run tests with a large and worldwide audience.\r\n\r\nGatling FrontLine will deploy your load injectors, close the instances after the test and aggregate your results live.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/5\" el_class=\"column_image_open_source no_radius\"][vc_single_image image=\"462\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"image_open_source\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"row_bottom_solutions\"][vc_column width=\"3/5\" el_class=\"column_image_enterprise\"][vc_single_image image=\"463\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" el_class=\"image_enterprise\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/5\" el_class=\"column_text_enterprise\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_enterprise\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_enterprise\">On-demand load injectors</h2>\r\n<p class=\"desc_enterprise\">With Gatling FrontLine, you can deploy your load injectors on on-demand instances. We support most of the cloud providers of the market: Amazon Web Services, Google Cloud Platform, Microsoft Azure, Digital Ocean and the cloud providers based on OpenStack (Rackspace, OVH…). We also support OpenShift and Kubernetes deployments. Gatling FrontLine will do everything: open the instance, close the instance after the test and aggregate the results. You configure everything through Gatling FrontLine’s interface.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"row_top_solutions\"][vc_column width=\"2/5\" el_class=\"column_text_open_source\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_open_source\"]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_open_source\">Clustering/Distributed mode</h2>\r\nWith Gatling FrontLine’s clustering (or distributed) mode, you can run tests with a large and worldwide audience.\r\n\r\nGatling FrontLine will deploy your load injectors, close the instances after the test and aggregate your results live.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/5\" el_class=\"column_image_open_source no_radius\"][vc_single_image image=\"464\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"image_open_source\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"section_table_get_started\"][vc_row el_class=\"row_table_get_started\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 class=\"title_table_get_started\" style=\"text-align: center;\">What are the differences</h2>\r\n<p class=\"sub_title_table_get_started\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Between Gatling Open Source and Gatling Frontline?</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html el_class=\"row_inner_table_differences\"]JTVCdGFibGUlMjBpZCUzRDElMjAlMkYlNUQ=[/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_convinced\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Are you convinced ?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Go ahead and try Gatling Frontline for free!</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\"][vc_column_inner el_class=\"column_button_convinced\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_btn title=\"Start your evaluation\" align=\"right\" el_class=\"violet_button\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"column_button_convinced\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_btn title=\"Watch demo\" i_icon_fontawesome=\"far fa-play-circle\" add_icon=\"true\" el_class=\"white_button_with_border\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"section_newsletter\"][vc_row el_class=\"row_newsletter\"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_newsletter_top\"]\r\n<p class=\"title_newsletter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Stay in the know!</p>\r\n<p class=\"join_newsletter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Join 10K+ subscribers to our newsletter.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column][rt_cf7_style radiant_extra_class=\"newsletter_form\"][contact-form-7 id=\"123\"][/rt_cf7_style][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text el_class=\"text_newsletter_bottom\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Gatling Corp needs the contact information you provide to us to contact you about our products and services. You may unsubscribe from these communications at any time. For information on how to unsubscribe, as well as our privacy practices and commitment to protecting your privacy, please review our Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]', 'Gatling Enterprise', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '430-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-04-15 15:10:15', '2021-04-15 13:10:15', '', 430, 'http://localhost/Sharing/Gatling/base-wordpress/?p=476', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
